### ============================================

### ✅ Test C1: Legitimate Request (safe) → expect 1 row
GET {{server}}/odata/v4/admin/fetchCustomer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}

{
  "customerID": "1004100",
  "method": "safe"
